author: Kynix @KynixXBT
text: $PUMP just launched. Did not manage to get into the presale so sidelined here. Good 1.3-1.5x for all those who made it in. But I don't think it has higher to go at all. Quite a crowded trade. Considering it's 5-6 Billion FDV with no utility, the upside seems very limited.
